def calculate_max_wins(test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (n, my_crew, rival_crew) = case
        my_crew.sort(reverse=True)
        rival_crew.sort(reverse=True)
        j = 1
        k = 0
        while k < n:
            if my_crew[j] > rival_crew[k]:
                j += 1
            k += 1
        results.append(j)
    return results
